lines.speaker: Teacher
lines.zh: 这节课是学校组织的职业规划辅导。
lines.en: This class is part of the school’s career planning program.

lines.speaker: Teacher
lines.zh: 让你们写的未来职业规划，都写好了吗？
lines.en: Have you all finished writing your career plans?

lines.speaker: Teacher
lines.zh: 第一批参加辅导的同学，拿着写好的东西到门口集合。
lines.en: The first group going for counseling, bring your plans and gather at the door.
